title: FIXED - John Barrowman Music Collection
description:
A \"mostly complete\" collection of John Barrowman\&#039;s music including

Studio Albums
-Another Side
-Born To Be Me
-Reflections From Broadway

Soundtracks
-Aspects of Andrew Lloyd Webber (incomplete)
-The Fix (incomplete)
-Phantom

Plus a bunch of misc. songs from Grease, West Side Story, The Kennedy Center Honors, etc.

Collected and ripped from various places over the last few years.

Albums are ripped at 128 or higher
Live (fan recorded or TV audio rip) may have background noise or be moderate to poor quality.

Enjoy!
